\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1 2.    Initialize Application\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 Create a folder called "onlinedatingapp"\par
